# Development-only environment settings for KQode.
# Copy this file to `.env` if you need local dev toggles. `.env` is gitignored.
#
# Provider credentials, models, and base URLs are configured with `/login` and
# `/model`; API keys are stored in the OS keychain, not in `.env`.

# Optional: force LLM request/response logging to ~/.kqode/logs/. Logging is ON
# by default in dev builds and OFF in packaged builds; uncomment to force it on
# (dist opt-in), or set to 0 to turn it off in dev. The TUI `--debug` flag sets
# this for you. API keys are never written to the logs.
# KQODE_DEBUG=1
